20240111 회의

필요한 DB테이블

- USER 테이블(
 NAME VARCHAR(50)	
 ID VARCHAR(50)   	-> primary key
 PW VARCHAR(50)
 EMAIL VARCHAR(50)
 ADDRESS VARCHAR(50)
 BIRTH VARCHAR(50)
 PET(50)
)

- ADMIN 테이블(
 ID VARCHAR(50)
 PW VARCHAR(50)

)
